#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:4
msgid "About Free Software and the GPL"
msgstr "Des logiciels libres et de la licence GPL "

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:9
msgid ""
"When one hears about \"free software\", the first thing that comes to mind "
"might be \"no cost\". While this is typically true, the term \"free software"
"\" as used by the Free Software Foundation (originators of the GNU Project "
"and creators of the GNU General Public License) is intended to mean \"free "
"as in freedom\" rather than the \"no cost\" sense (which is usually "
"referred to as \"free as in free beer\" or *gratis*). Free software in this "
"sense is software which you are free to use, copy, modify, redistribute, "
"with no limit. Contrast this with the licensing of most commercial software "
"packages, where you are allowed to load the software on a single computer, "
"are allowed to make no copies, and never see the source code. Free software "
"allows incredible freedom to the end user. Since the source code is "
"universally available, there are also many more chances for bugs to be "
"caught and fixed."
msgstr ""
"Vous pouvez utiliser, copier, modifier, et redistribuer, sans limite les "
"logiciels libres. Il faut savoir que la plupart des licences de logiciels "
"propriétaires ne vous autorisent qu'une seule installation et vous "
"interdisent toute copie et consultation du code source. Les logiciels "
"libres procurent une grande indépendance à l'utilisateur final. Les bogues "
"ont beaucoup plus de chance d'être repérés et corrigés car le code source "
"est visible par tous."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:21
msgid ""
"When a program is licensed under the GNU General Public License (the GPL):"
msgstr ""
"Quand un programme est distribué sous licence GPL (*GNU General Public "
"License*, licence publique générale), vous avez le droit de :"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:23
msgid "You have the right to use the program for any purpose."
msgstr "l'utiliser à n'importe quelle fin"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:24
msgid ""
"You have the right to modify the program, and have access to the source "
"codes."
msgstr "le modifier et accéder au code source"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:25
msgid "You have the right to copy and distribute the program."
msgstr "copier et distribuer le programme"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:26
msgid ""
"You have the right to improve the program, and release your own versions."
msgstr "l'améliorer, et publier vos propres versions"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:28
msgid ""
"In return for these rights, you have some responsibilities if you "
"distribute a GPL'd program, responsibilities that are designed to protect "
"your freedoms and the freedoms of others:"
msgstr ""
"En retour, si vous distribuez un logiciel sous licence GPL, afin de "
"préserver vos droits et ceux des autres, vous avez quelques responsabilités:"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:31
msgid ""
"You must provide a copy of the GPL with the program, so that recipients are "
"aware of their rights under the license."
msgstr ""
"vous devez fournir une licence GPL avec votre logiciel, afin que les "
"utilisateurs de votre programme soient informés de leurs droits quant au "
"logiciel"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:33
msgid ""
"You must include the source code or make the source code freely available."
msgstr ""
"vous devez inclure le code source ou faire en sorte qu'il soit gratuitement "
"disponible"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:34
msgid ""
"If you modify the code and distribute the modified version, you must "
"license your modifications available under the GPL (or a compatible "
"license)."
msgstr ""
"si vous modifiez le code et distribuez votre version du logiciel, vous "
"devez mettre vos modifications sous licence GPL (ou une licence compatible)"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:36
msgid ""
"You may not restrict the licensing of the program beyond the terms of the "
"GPL. (you may not turn a GPL'd program into a proprietary product.)"
msgstr ""
"vous ne pouvez pas restreindre la licence d'un logiciel GNU GPL (vous ne "
"pouvez pas transformer un logiciel GPL en un produit propriétaire)"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:39
msgid ""
"For more on the GPL, check the its page on the `GNU Project web site "
"<https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses.html#GPL>`__."
msgstr ""
"Pour de plus amples informations sur la licence GPL, vous pouvez consulter "
"`le site du projet GNU (en) <https://www.gnu.org/licenses/licenses."
"html#GPL>`__."

#: ../../manual/getting_started/about_blender/license.rst:44
msgid ""
"The GPL only applies to the Blender application and **not** the artwork you "
"create with it; for more info see the `Blender License <http://www.blender."
"org/about/license/>`__."
msgstr ""
"La licence GPL s'applique seulement au programme Blender et **non** aux "
"œuvres que vous créez avec; pour plus d'information consulter `la licence "
"de Blender (en) <http://www.blender.org/about/license/>`__.\t"
